# Privacy Policy - Doped YouTube Extension

**Last Updated:** January 2025

## TL;DR
This extension does NOT collect, store, or transmit any of your personal data. Everything runs locally in your browser.

## 1. Information We Do NOT Collect

This extension does NOT collect, store, or transmit:
- Your browsing history
- Your personal information
- Your YouTube viewing habits
- Any data about videos you watch
- Your IP address or location
- Any authentication tokens or credentials

## 2. Data Storage

The extension stores the following data **locally on your device only** using Chrome's storage API:
- **Settings:** Your preferences (e.g., enable/disable features, color preferences)
- **Statistics:** Local counters (ads blocked, videos watched) - stored only on your device

**This data never leaves your computer.**

## 3. Permissions Explanation

The extension requires the following permissions to function:
- **storage:** To save your settings and statistics locally
- **declarativeNetRequest:** To block ads and unwanted content on YouTube
- **tabs:** To detect when you're on YouTube pages and apply enhancements
- **scripting:** To inject features like PiP, speed controls, and audio mode
- **Host permissions (*.youtube.com, *.googlevideo.com):** To modify YouTube pages and video streams

## 4. Third-Party Services

The extension may connect to:
- **returnyoutubedislikeapi.com:** To fetch dislike counts for YouTube videos (if enabled)

This is an optional feature that can be disabled in settings. No personal data is sent to this API.

## 5. Ad Blocking

The extension blocks ads on YouTube using local rules. No data about blocked ads is sent anywhere. All processing happens locally in your browser.

## 6. Data Sharing

**We do NOT share any data with third parties because we don't collect any data in the first place.**

## 7. Children's Privacy

This extension does not knowingly collect any information from children under 13 years of age. Since we don't collect any data at all, the extension is safe for all ages.

## 8. Changes to Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date.

## 9. Open Source Transparency

This extension's code is transparent and can be reviewed. All functionality is contained within the extension files with no external code execution or data collection.

## 10. Contact

If you have questions about this privacy policy or the extension's functionality, you can review the extension's code or contact us through the Chrome Web Store listing.

## Summary

**Your privacy is 100% protected.** This extension:
- ✅ Does NOT collect any personal data
- ✅ Does NOT track your browsing
- ✅ Does NOT send data to external servers
- ✅ Stores settings only locally on your device
- ✅ Works entirely offline (except for optional dislike API)
